OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pedestrian hit by car
OL,6,FA driver has been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder after a pedestrian
OL,8,Fwas hit by a car outside Hastings
OL,9,Frailway station.
OL,11,FBritish Transport Police say officers
OL,12,Fwere called at 4.13pm on Wednesday 8
OL,13,FJuly, to reports that a car had struck
OL,14,Fa pedestrian.
OL,16,FParamedics also attended and a 47-year-
OL,17,Fold man was taken to hospital with
OL,18,Flife-threatening injuries.
OL,20,FHe remains there in a critical
OL,21,Fcondition.
