OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pedestrian hit by car
OL,6,FA man was arrested nearby and BTP
OL,7,Fdetectives have now charged Lee
OL,8,FMcGreevy, who's 48 and of Hastings,
OL,9,Fwith attempted murder.
OL,11,FHe was remanded in custody to appear
OL,12,Fat Brighton Magistrates' Court today
OL,13,F(10 July).
OL,15,FAny witnesses who haven't already
OL,16,Fspoken to police are asked to contact
OL,17,FBTP by texting 61016 or calling 0800
OL,18,F40 50 40, quoting reference 552 of 8
OL,19,FJuly.
